    "description": "Being Holdings Co., Ltd., together with its subsidiaries, operates as a logistics and transportation company in Japan. It operates through Logistics Business and Others segments. The company offers third-party logistics services, including transportation, storage, packaging, handling, distribution, processing, and information system development, as well as logistics consulting services. It also provides passenger transportation services, including ride-hailing services. In addition, the company operates taxis, charter buses, chartered sightseeing taxis, VIP and wedding hire cars, and location buses. Further, it offers travel services; maintenance, customization, and support services for information systems; insurance agency services; vehicle inspection and general maintenance services for light vehicles and cargo trucks; consultation services for purchasing new and used cars; gas stations; and leasing services for logistics centers and other real estate properties. Being Holdings Co., Ltd. was incorporated in 1986 and is headquartered in Kanazawa, Japan."
